'''約瑟夫·勒杜克斯'''（{{bd|1949年|12月7日|}}，{{lang-en|Joseph E. LeDoux}}）是一位[[美國|美國]]的[[神經科學家|神經科學家]]，其研究主要集中於生存迴路，包括對諸如[[恐懼|恐懼]]和[[焦慮|焦慮]]之類的情緒的影響。<ref>"I'm not studying emotion. I'm studying the function of survival circuits. Survival circuits contribute to emotions but are not emotion circuits." LeDoux as quoted in: {{cite web |last=Emory |first=Margaret |date=June 6, 2018 |title=On Fear, Emotions, and Memory: An Interview with Dr. Joseph LeDoux |url=https://brainworldmagazine.com/on-fear-emotions-and-memory-an-interview-with-dr-joseph-ledoux/ |website=brainworldmagazine.com |access-date=2020-04-05}}</ref>

